In this scene Barry (CW) told his name was "The Flash", so Barry (DCEU) responded questioningly "The Flash?.. The Flash.." like he would use that as his codename.

Then Barry (DCEU) went back to Victor

Victor: So I'm Cyborg. What is your codename?
Barry: The Flash!
Victor: You came up with that yourself?
Flash: Kind of..

And he said "Kind of" because Barry Allen (CW) came up with that name and they are actually the same....

AHHHHHHH This is no coincidence
